content:
Use Visibility Rules to Manage What Buyers See

Customize the content that buyers see when switching accounts using expression-based visibility rules. Improve user experience and increase engagement by choosing which information is visible to different buyers.

Where: This change applies to B2B Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: In Experience Builder, select the component that you want to customize, and add the visibility rule to the component.
title: Customizing B2B Commerce Visibility Rules
